&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join our Outpatient team working at The Countess of Chester Hospital and at Ellesmere Port Hospital. We are looking to recruit an experienced nurse who has experience in leg ulcer management,micro-suctioning, dermatology patch testing or has had IRMER training.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Outpatients covers multiple specialities, both medical and surgical and we are looking to recruit a nurse who will rotate between all specialities.Experinece in leg ulcer management, micro-suctioning, patch testing or xray ordering is desirable, however full training will be given. Previous experience of Outpatients is also desirable, however is not essential.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
